node.text:
We had the best time this weekend at the #NYTFoodFestival eating incredible food from @leonellinyc @morgansternsnyc @marcforgione and more!
The @nytimes & @nytlive brought together some of NYC’s best restaurants and vendors for two special days of food in Bryant Park and we already can’t wait until next year 😝
#newforkcity
